    {
      "id": "security-items",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 115,
      "y": 722,
      "width": 310,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "🔑 KMS CMK — RDS, SSM, S3, SNS, CloudTrail\n📋 CloudTrail — API audit logs (90d retention)\n🔒 SSM Parameter Store — DB_URL, JWT_SECRET\n📊 CloudWatch — Dashboard + 6 Alarms\n👤 IAM — Least-privilege roles + GitHub OIDC",
