      "originalText": "🔑 KMS CMK — RDS, SSM, S3, SNS, CloudTrail\n📋 CloudTrail — API audit logs (90d retention)\n🔒 SSM Parameter Store — DB_URL, JWT_SECRET\n📊 CloudWatch — Dashboard + 6 Alarms\n👤 IAM — Least-privilege roles + GitHub OIDC",
