      "y": 722,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "RDS PostgreSQL ............... $13.50\nS3 + CloudFront ................ $2.00\nLambda (API + Scraper) ......... $0.50\nAPI Gateway + ECR + KMS ........ $2.00\nCloudWatch + VPC Endpoints ..... $1.00\n─────────────────────────\nTotal                         ~$17/mo",
